text: Marcelo Tomás Barrios Vera and Nicolás Jarry were the defending champions but only Barrios Vera chose to defend his title, partnering José Hernández- Fernández. Barrios Vera lost in the semifinals to Romain Arneodo and Jonathan Eysseric. Arneodo and Eysseric won the title after defeating Guido Andreozzi and Guillermo Durán 7–6(7–4), 1–6, [12–10] in the final. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== * Main Draw Challenger ATP Cachantún Cup - Doubles 2018 Doubles
